{"tid":145214,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"路邊渠蓋大翻新　網民狠批好醜樣","createTime":"2017-03-06T05:47:06.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-06T07:48:11.000Z","uid":41343,"like":0,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"008957ac6cf48b1ac5b67b4debf1ff332b1c3f31","tid":145214,"uid":41343,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-06T05:47:06.000Z","msg":"文化界名人彭志銘近日在facebook上分享了幾張照片，拍攝了路邊新渠蓋的外觀。相中可見渠蓋由黑色直條坑洞，換成銀色格狀渠蓋，外觀分別很大。&nbsp;<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n不少網民對新渠蓋似乎不太受落，狠批「核突」。有人形容新渠蓋像燒烤網，又質疑賊人會否更容易撬起偷走變賣。也有人認為嘥錢，擔心新款渠蓋比舊蓋更易出意外。但另有網民為新渠蓋平反，認為新蓋的坑洞更細小，手機鎖匙等物件，以及單車車輪或高踭鞋等不易「攝入去」，保障安全。亦有人指換不換都一樣要飽受批評，表示「左右做人難」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20170305/photo/bkn-20170305170859312-0305_00822_001_01p.jpg?20170305172025\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20170305%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20170305170859312-0305_00822_001_01p.jpg%3F20170305172025&h=b900e66e&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"dceca00144ff151afcd9ead913fa4a5d22739239","tid":145214,"uid":69568,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-06T06:04:02.000Z","msg":"強逼症嗰d gg"},{"pid":"ec59e3a8b7596c8cb70471f06fbc9bac06563d30","tid":145214,"uid":31098,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-06T06:04:36.000Z","msg":"喺灣仔見過，我仲為係臨時頂住先 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n個 design 好地地做乜要換，仲要換成咁樣衰嘅 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c30aef7a46fd7712afb9b574144f78879de8972a","tid":145214,"uid":25148,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-06T06:13:59.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>強逼症嗰d gg</blockquote><br />\n又點good game<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2a2a5485e86fdb75bf795d9b7037001d21d3a335","tid":145214,"uid":25148,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":